<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>م ج د<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٧٤٣ - م ج د]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>استمجدَ يسْتمجد، استمجادًا، فهو مُستمجِد، والمفعول مُستمجَد <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• استمجدَ الشَّخصُ:</span> طلبَ المجدَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• استمجدَ ضيفَه:</span> وجده ماجدًا <span class="c1">"استمجده فقدّره حقّ قدره"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>